==English==
===Etymology===
The name of [[w:Gertrude Stein|Gertrude Stein]]'s lover, who included cannabis in a recipe for fudge published in 1954.

===Noun phrase===
{{en-noun|sg=[[w:Alice B. Toklas|Alice B. Toklas]] [[brownie]]}}

# A sweet [[cake]] or [[biscuit]] made with [[cannabis]].

